605
00:34:37.200 --> 00:34:38.910  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Computer, open Sick Bay doors.</c.bg_transparent>

606
00:34:38.993 --> 00:34:40.328  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i><c.bg_transparent>Unable to comply.</c.bg_transparent></i>

607
00:34:43.164 --> 00:34:45.958  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Override.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Authorization: Tuvok-pi-alpha.</c.bg_transparent>

608
00:34:46.042 --> 00:34:47.835  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i><c.bg_transparent>Authorization denied.</c.bg_transparent></i>

609
00:34:53.549 --> 00:34:54.967  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Doctor, stop what you're doing.</c.bg_transparent>

610
00:34:55.051 --> 00:34:56.677  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're interrupting</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a medical procedure.</c.bg_transparent>

611
00:34:58.096 --> 00:34:59.388  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Your program has been altered.</c.bg_transparent>

612
00:35:00.431 --> 00:35:02.183  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-What do you mean, altered?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Ignore him.</c.bg_transparent>

613
00:35:02.266 --> 00:35:04.268  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>B'Elanna, this is completely irrational.</c.bg_transparent>

614
00:35:04.936 --> 00:35:07.063  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Will someone please tell me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>what's going on?</c.bg_transparent>

615
00:35:07.146 --> 00:35:09.732  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm your patient.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Your first duty is to me and my baby.</c.bg_transparent>

616
00:35:10.650 --> 00:35:12.318  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Tuvok to Bridge.</c.bg_transparent>
<i><c.bg_transparent>-Kim here.</c.bg_transparent></i>

617
00:35:12.401 --> 00:35:13.820  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's a force field in Sick Bay.</c.bg_transparent>

618
00:35:14.237 --> 00:35:15.238  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can't deactivate it.</c.bg_transparent>

619
00:35:15.321 --> 00:35:18.116  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Cut power to the EPS relay</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>surrounding the Surgical Bay.</c.bg_transparent>

620
00:35:19.450 --> 00:35:22.120  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Access has been restricted.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'll have to bypass them.</c.bg_transparent>

621
00:35:22.203 --> 00:35:24.914  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You said it could be dangerous</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to delay the procedure.</c.bg_transparent>

622
00:35:24.997 --> 00:35:27.834  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>She's manipulating you, doc,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in more ways than one.</c.bg_transparent>

623
00:35:27.917 --> 00:35:30.419  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sorry, but if there's something</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>wrong with my program.</c.bg_transparent>

624
00:35:30.503 --> 00:35:32.505  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's nothing wrong</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with your program!</c.bg_transparent>

625
00:35:32.588 --> 00:35:35.341  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>[Kim]</c.bg_transparent>
<i><c.bg_transparent>I'm cutting power to the Surgical Bay now.</c.bg_transparent></i>

626
00:35:39.720 --> 00:35:41.472  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I suggest we deactivate your program,</c.bg_transparent>

627
00:35:41.556 --> 00:35:43.766  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>until we determine</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the extent of the alterations.</c.bg_transparent>

628
00:35:47.353 --> 00:35:48.354  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I understand.</c.bg_transparent>

629
00:35:49.272 --> 00:35:50.773  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Computer, deactivate EMH.</c.bg_transparent>

630
00:35:52.525 --> 00:35:53.943  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You had no right to interfere.</c.bg_transparent>

631
00:35:54.402 --> 00:35:56.696  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tuvok, would you mind</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>giving us a minute?</c.bg_transparent>

632
00:36:02.660 --> 00:36:05.204  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I never thought</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you would go this far.</c.bg_transparent>

633
00:36:05.913 --> 00:36:09.292  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I don't know what you're talking about.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Reprogramming the doctor?</c.bg_transparent>

634
00:36:09.375 --> 00:36:11.419  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I upgraded his program,</c.bg_transparent>

635
00:36:11.502 --> 00:36:13.629  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>so he could understand</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>what had to be done.</c.bg_transparent>

636
00:36:13.713 --> 00:36:15.756  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You mean to reconfigure our baby</c.bg_transparent>

637
00:36:16.507 --> 00:36:18.384  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>so she wouldn't be</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>treated like a monster.</c.bg_transparent>

638
00:36:18.467 --> 00:36:20.553  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's not just about the way</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>she'll be treated!</c.bg_transparent>

639
00:36:21.721 --> 00:36:23.389  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What else is it about, then?!</c.bg_transparent>

640
00:36:24.557 --> 00:36:27.268  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Come on, B'Elanna, tell me!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Forget it.</c.bg_transparent>

641
00:36:27.351 --> 00:36:31.022  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, no. We're not going to forget it.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>We're going to talk about this right now.</c.bg_transparent>

642
00:36:31.105 --> 00:36:33.566  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Stop telling me what to do!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You're not my father!</c.bg_transparent>

643
00:36:38.779 --> 00:36:40.239  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What are you talking about?</c.bg_transparent>

644
00:36:43.201 --> 00:36:44.827  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Look, my fath...</c.bg_transparent>

645
00:36:46.662 --> 00:36:48.664  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What? What about him?</c.bg_transparent>

646
00:36:51.292 --> 00:36:52.835  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, we were inseparable.</c.bg_transparent>

647
00:36:54.837 --> 00:36:56.839  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He spoiled me and I worshipped him,</c.bg_transparent>

648
00:36:58.674 --> 00:36:59.717  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>but the older I got...</c.bg_transparent>

649
00:37:02.011 --> 00:37:03.137  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>...we just grew apart.</c.bg_transparent>

650
00:37:06.182 --> 00:37:09.435  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He ended up organizing this camping trip</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with my cousins.</c.bg_transparent>

651
00:37:11.312 --> 00:37:12.605  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I guess he just wanted to--</c.bg_transparent>

652
00:37:14.023 --> 00:37:15.816  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't know</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>make things better again.</c.bg_transparent>

653
00:37:18.319 --> 00:37:19.946  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-But it didn't.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-It was awful.</c.bg_transparent>

654
00:37:23.157 --> 00:37:24.742  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I ended up trying to run away.</c.bg_transparent>

655
00:37:25.660 --> 00:37:28.663  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>B'Elanna? What are you doing?</c.bg_transparent>

656
00:37:29.956 --> 00:37:32.291  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It was so stupid.</c.bg_transparent>

657
00:37:32.375 --> 00:37:33.876  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I mean, where was I going to go?</c.bg_transparent>

658
00:37:36.462 --> 00:37:38.381  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You probably just</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>wanted him to stop you.</c.bg_transparent>

659
00:37:41.175 --> 00:37:42.176  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, he did.</c.bg_transparent>

660
00:37:43.761 --> 00:37:45.263  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't touch me.</c.bg_transparent>

661
00:37:45.346 --> 00:37:47.014  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>B'Elanna, what's wrong?</c.bg_transparent>

662
00:37:47.098 --> 00:37:49.100  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You know what's wrong.</c.bg_transparent>

663
00:37:49.183 --> 00:37:50.559  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, I don't.</c.bg_transparent>

664
00:37:51.394 --> 00:37:53.688  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Maybe I'm just being moody</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and unpredictable.</c.bg_transparent>

665
00:37:55.815 --> 00:37:57.483  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What are you talking about?</c.bg_transparent>

666
00:37:57.566 --> 00:37:59.402  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I heard what you said to Uncle Carl.</c.bg_transparent>

667
00:38:00.820 --> 00:38:01.821  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[sighs]</c.bg_transparent>

668
00:38:03.698 --> 00:38:05.491  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You shouldn't be listening</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to private conversations.</c.bg_transparent>

669
00:38:05.574 --> 00:38:08.327  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And you shouldn't have said</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>what you did about Mommy!</c.bg_transparent>

670
00:38:08.411 --> 00:38:09.704  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[sobs]</c.bg_transparent>

671
00:38:27.388 --> 00:38:28.848  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>B'Elanna, listen to me.</c.bg_transparent>

672
00:38:30.391 --> 00:38:32.893  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Your mother and I</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>are having problems but--</c.bg_transparent>

673
00:38:32.977 --> 00:38:34.186  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You don't love her anymore.</c.bg_transparent>

674
00:38:35.021 --> 00:38:37.606  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-That's not true.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Yes, it is, and you don't love me either.</c.bg_transparent>

675
00:38:38.441 --> 00:38:40.526  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-B'Elanna--</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-You're no different than anyone else.</c.bg_transparent>

676
00:38:40.609 --> 00:38:42.153  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You don't like Klingons. You said it.</c.bg_transparent>

677
00:38:42.611 --> 00:38:44.780  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You are twisting my words, B'Elanna.</c.bg_transparent>

678
00:38:45.281 --> 00:38:47.408  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Maybe he was right.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Maybe you misunderstood.</c.bg_transparent>

679
00:38:47.491 --> 00:38:48.743  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, I know what I heard.</c.bg_transparent>

680
00:38:49.785 --> 00:38:51.162  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It made me so angry!</c.bg_transparent>

681
00:38:51.245 --> 00:38:53.664  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You had a right to be,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>after the things he said.</c.bg_transparent>

682
00:38:54.123 --> 00:38:55.291  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's not what he said.</c.bg_transparent>

683
00:38:56.208 --> 00:38:57.376  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's what I said.</c.bg_transparent>

684
00:38:57.835 --> 00:39:00.880  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you can't stand living with us,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>then why don't you just leave?!</c.bg_transparent>

685
00:39:03.424 --> 00:39:04.717  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And that's exactly what he did.</c.bg_transparent>

686
00:39:06.177 --> 00:39:07.219  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, B'Elanna...</c.bg_transparent>

687
00:39:09.055 --> 00:39:10.264  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Twelve days later</c.bg_transparent>

688
00:39:11.766 --> 00:39:13.225  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and he never came back.</c.bg_transparent>

689
00:39:14.310 --> 00:39:16.270  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You can't blame yourself for that.</c.bg_transparent>

690
00:39:16.937 --> 00:39:17.980  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why not?</c.bg_transparent>

691
00:39:19.106 --> 00:39:23.944  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Because he was obviously</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>unhappy about his marriage.</c.bg_transparent>

692
00:39:24.028 --> 00:39:26.238  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He didn't leave</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>just because you told him to.</c.bg_transparent>

693
00:39:26.906 --> 00:39:28.157  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You don't know that.</c.bg_transparent>

694
00:39:30.451 --> 00:39:32.912  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Look, whatever the reason was,</c.bg_transparent>

695
00:39:34.372 --> 00:39:36.957  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sure it was a horrible thing</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for you to live with.</c.bg_transparent>

696
00:39:44.340 --> 00:39:45.883  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Wait a minute. You don't think...</c.bg_transparent>

697
00:39:47.385 --> 00:39:48.386  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[sighs]</c.bg_transparent>

698
00:39:49.428 --> 00:39:53.140  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>B'Elanna,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I am never going to leave you.</c.bg_transparent>

699
00:39:53.224 --> 00:39:54.475  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You say that now</c.bg_transparent>

700
00:39:56.102 --> 00:39:58.979  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but think about how hard it is</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to live with one Klingon.</c.bg_transparent>

701
00:39:59.063 --> 00:40:00.898  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pretty soon it'll be two.</c.bg_transparent>

702
00:40:00.981 --> 00:40:02.983  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And someday I hope it's three or four.</c.bg_transparent>

703
00:40:04.402 --> 00:40:09.240  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I mean it, and I hope that</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>every one of them is just like you.</c.bg_transparent>

704
00:40:12.284 --> 00:40:13.452  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>B'Elanna...</c.bg_transparent>

705
00:40:14.078 --> 00:40:18.249  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I am not your father,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and you are not your mother,</c.bg_transparent>

706
00:40:19.458 --> 00:40:21.001  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and our daughter</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>is going to be perfect</c.bg_transparent>

707
00:40:21.085 --> 00:40:23.003  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>just the way she is.</c.bg_transparent>

708
00:40:23.879 --> 00:40:24.880  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You really think so?</c.bg_transparent>

709
00:40:26.715 --> 00:40:27.883  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know so.</c.bg_transparent>

710
00:40:38.144 --> 00:40:42.815  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>[doctor]</c.bg_transparent>
<i><c.bg_transparent>Medical Officer's Log, Stardate 54452.6.</c.bg_transparent></i>

711
00:40:42.898 --> 00:40:45.651  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i><c.bg_transparent>Lieutenant Torres</c.bg_transparent></i>
<i><c.bg_transparent>has deleted the alterations</c.bg_transparent></i>

712
00:40:45.734 --> 00:40:47.486  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i><c.bg_transparent>she made to my program.</c.bg_transparent></i>

713
00:40:47.570 --> 00:40:50.156  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i><c.bg_transparent>It's a relief to be back</c.bg_transparent></i>
<i><c.bg_transparent>to my old self again.</c.bg_transparent></i>

714
00:40:51.323 --> 00:40:53.242  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Good morning, Lieutenant.</c.bg_transparent>

715
00:40:53.325 --> 00:40:55.077  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-You're not feeling ill, are you?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-No.</c.bg_transparent>

716
00:40:55.786 --> 00:40:56.787  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm fine.</c.bg_transparent>

717
00:40:58.372 --> 00:41:02.793  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I just wanted to apologize</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for violating your program.</c.bg_transparent>

718
00:41:06.755 --> 00:41:07.798  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Apology accepted.</c.bg_transparent>

719
00:41:08.966 --> 00:41:11.677  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not guilty by reason of biochemistry.</c.bg_transparent>

720
00:41:13.929 --> 00:41:15.598  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Nice of you to let me off the hook,</c.bg_transparent>

721
00:41:17.308 --> 00:41:19.143  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>but biochemistry isn't an excuse.</c.bg_transparent>

722
00:41:20.895 --> 00:41:22.563  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I knew exactly what I was doing.</c.bg_transparent>

723
00:41:25.816 --> 00:41:27.276  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[gasps]</c.bg_transparent>

724
00:41:27.359 --> 00:41:28.736  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is something wrong?</c.bg_transparent>

725
00:41:29.778 --> 00:41:31.155  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't know.</c.bg_transparent>

726
00:41:36.577 --> 00:41:37.661  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Your baby's kicking.</c.bg_transparent>

727
00:41:39.371 --> 00:41:41.707  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-So soon?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Well, she is part Klingon.</c.bg_transparent>

