00:41:48.714 --> 00:41:49.965  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>May I?</c.bg_transparent>

731
00:41:55.012 --> 00:41:56.972  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>[both exhale]</c.bg_transparent>

732
00:41:57.056 --> 00:41:58.307  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Feisty little thing, isn't she?</c.bg_transparent>

733
00:41:59.266 --> 00:42:00.601  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I wonder where she gets that from.</c.bg_transparent>

734
00:42:01.644 --> 00:42:04.730  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Speaking of the baby,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I have another request.</c.bg_transparent>

735
00:42:05.272 --> 00:42:06.273  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes?</c.bg_transparent>

736
00:42:08.901 --> 00:42:10.736  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
