<c.bg_transparent>kids than Harry, and if you think--</c.bg_transparent>

739
00:42:20.079 --> 00:42:21.580  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I accept.</c.bg_transparent>

740
00:42:22.456 --> 00:42:23.499  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thanks.</c.bg_transparent>

741
00:42:24.917 --> 00:42:26.168  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thank you.</c.bg_transparent>

742
00:42:27.127 --> 00:42:28.504  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was also wondering...</c.bg_transparent>

743
